Description: Python game-development base stack for Foundry Linux
 Essential and recommended Python libraries for game development on
 Foundry Linux. Covers the full game-dev toolchain:
 .
   * Game frameworks  pygame, pyglet, python3-opengl, python3-glfw
   * Math/science     numpy, scipy, numba, shapely
   * Image            pillow, imageio
   * Audio            sounddevice, soundfile, pydub
   * Config/data      pyyaml, tomli, tomli-w, msgpack, lz4
   * Networking       websockets, aiohttp, pyzmq, aiosqlite
   * Dev tools        click, rich, tqdm, pytest, mypy, loguru, psutil,
                      ruff, cython3
 .
 For audio analysis (beat detection, spectrograms) and screenshot
 capture install foundry-python-gamedev-extras as well.
